{
  "stem": "6159.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But under the German law, she was considered Polish.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she already married the second husband when this happened, and because of the first husband, she was searched everywhere because they wanted to take her out of the country as-- as a non-Hungarian, and she was running every night to a different friend or-- or neighbor's place not to find her because she already had a chart.",
      "word_count": 58
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From the second husband who was taken away to-- to Russia.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So the-- then she had to-- to apply every week to this particular-- people who was in the office for-- for this purpose who was running away to the foreigners, let's call it, and she had to report every week.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But then after she started to disappear, started to go places where they couldn't find her because she never got a permanent-- they didn't give her to live there permanently in Hungary.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And, finally, I think that she had to pay somebody something, and they-- they allowed her to stay and that's when she settled down.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Then, after, of course, she was looking for me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was taken away, and she was there with a child and no husband.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she had some little money left and she bought a Swiss passport for me.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But by the time, it reached me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It would have reached each me, I was taken away to a hospital with dysentery.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From the working camp because I got that sickness which was contagious and, of course, they were afraid not only for the inmates, but that-- for themselves who was taking care of us.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So they ship me to a hospital where there were only men, soldiers.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's at-- It's called Daily [INAUDIBLE], it's-- it's very-- very close.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's-- it's the 13th precinct.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
